comments: Davis (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Holiday (MIL) and makes clean ball contact on his block attempt.
Hield (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Connaughton (MIL) and any body contact prior to the start of his upward shooting motion is deemed marginal.
Davis (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Holiday (MIL) and makes clean hand on ball contact to block the shot.
Holiday (MIL) draws Hield (SAC) into the air towards him and the contact results in a foul on Hield (SAC) even if contact is initiated by Holiday (MIL).
Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Holiday's (MIL) path and absorbs the contact.
Barnes (SAC) and Lopez (MIL) engage and disengage off ball in the post and the contact is marginal as it does not affect Lopez's ability to get to the entry pass.

Davis (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Connaughton (MIL) during the drive and cleanly dislodges the ball. Connaughton dives to the ground to retrieve the loose ball and MIL is granted a timeout before Fox (SAC) gets his hands on the ball.
Lopez (MIL) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Hield (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Holiday (MIL).
Barnes (SAC) slips the pick and starts his roll to the basket, when Holiday (MIL) simultaneously goes under the pick and incidental contact occurs as they come together.
Fox (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Holiday (MIL) at the end of the drive and cleanly pokes the ball loose.
Holiday (MIL) recovers the loose ball and then Barnes (SAC) makes clean ball contact to dislodge the ball again from Holiday on the steal.
Middleton (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Haliburton (SAC).
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on DiVincenzo (MIL).
DiVincenzo (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Fox (SAC).
Middleton (MIL) maintains a legal pivot foot and is granted his timeout request near the baseline.
Haliburton (SAC) commits a take foul on Connaughton (MIL).
Holiday (MIL) extends his arm out to poke the ball loose and any contact to Fox's (SAC) arm is deemed marginal as it does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Connaughton (MIL).
Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in DiVincenzo's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs as DiVincenzo jumps to try and deflect the inbound pass.
